You should go wash up first.

106
00:08:00,750 --> 00:08:01,990
My dear.

107
00:08:02,430 --> 00:08:04,190
I'll go wash up first.

108
00:08:04,190 --> 00:08:04,720
Go ahead.

109
00:08:06,030 --> 00:08:07,350
