141
00:11:26,070 --> 00:11:26,590
Okay.

142
00:11:26,630 --> 00:11:27,870
Well, I won't stand on ceremony.

143
00:11:27,870 --> 00:11:29,400
I'll sleep in your bedroom.

144
00:11:29,670 --> 00:11:30,430
Good night.

145
