149
00:11:45,270 --> 00:11:46,350
What do you mean?

150
00:11:47,950 --> 00:11:49,590
If we can get up later,

151
00:11:49,590 --> 00:11:51,150
we can then

152
00:11:51,150 --> 00:11:52,600
