153
00:11:55,790 --> 00:11:57,110
You...

154
00:11:59,350 --> 00:12:00,230
Oh, yeah.

155
00:12:25,670 --> 00:12:26,550
Good morning.

156
00:12:30,910 --> 00:12:32,270
You're up.

157
00:12:33,830 --> 00:12:34,890
Did you sleep well?

158
00:12:39,470 --> 00:12:41,580
I seem to love you more today

159
00:12:41,580 --> 00:12:42,600
