are indeed different.

180
00:14:16,190 --> 00:14:18,230
Well, it depends on who you are seeing.

181
00:14:18,230 --> 00:14:19,160
Come on, tell me.

182
00:14:19,190 --> 00:14:20,520
What's the difference?

183
00:14:23,070 --> 00:14:24,750
Let me analyze it for you.

184
00:14:24,990 --> 00:14:26,600
Generally speaking,

185
00:14:26,600 --> 00:14:27,750
capable people

186
00:14:27,750 --> 00:14:29,190
are not necessarily gentle.

187
00:14:29,190 --> 00:14:30,990
