189
00:14:33,790 --> 00:14:35,110
Being considerate doesn't necessarily mean you're pretty.

190
00:14:35,110 --> 00:14:37,550
Those who are pretty may not actually have good temperament.

191
00:14:37,550 --> 00:14:39,200
But my girl

192
00:14:39,270 --> 00:14:41,510
is good at everything.

193
00:14:41,510 --> 00:14:42,110
Enough.

194
00:14:42,390 --> 00:14:43,790
I won't ask ever again.

195
00:14:44,470 --> 00:14:45,390
By the way, Yao,

196
00:14:45,470 --> 00:14:45,990
tonight,

197
00:14:45,990 --> 00:14:46,790
I'm going to treat a pro

198
00:14:46,790 --> 00:14:47,550
from Hangzhou.

199
00:14:47,550 --> 00:14:48,470
Come with me.

200
00:14:48,470 --> 00:14:49,720
Help me hold up the fort.

201
00:14:49,720 --> 00:14:51,450
No, I already have a date today.

202
00:14:51,470 --> 00:14:53,200
Come on, is it your girlfriend?

203
00:15:03,470 --> 00:15:04,550
Hold onto my board for me.

204
00:15:04,550 --> 00:15:07,150
So much for putting his lover over his buddies.

205
00:15:08,910 --> 00:15:09,750
Tong Xin.

206
00:15:10,550 --> 00:15:12,870
If you still want to talk about the job-hopping,

207
00:15:12,870 --> 00:15:14,470
I can only say I'm sorry.

208
00:15:17,350 --> 00:15:19,120
Do you know Ms. Pan Jinyu?

209
00:15:19,270 --> 00:15:20,150
Yes.

210
00:15:20,390 --> 00:15:21,620
He is the only person in the world

211
00:15:21,620 --> 00:15:22,190
who knows

212
00:15:22,190 --> 00:15:23,510
the Pazeh language.

213
00:15:24,030 --> 00:15:24,670
Unfortunately,

214
00:15:24,670 --> 00:15:25,430
he passed away

215
00:15:25,430 --> 00:15:26,390
in 2010.

216
00:15:26,590 --> 00:15:27,430
In this world,

217
00:15:27,500 --> 00:15:29,590
no one else knows this language anymore.

218
00:15:29,590 --> 00:15:31,070
I was too young back then.

219
00:15:31,070 --> 00:15:33,590
Otherwise, I would have asked her to be my master.

220
00:15:33,590 --> 00:15:35,390
Would you have been able to do so?

221
00:15:37,790 --> 00:15:39,250
Let me show you something.

222
00:15:43,310 --> 00:15:45,350
This is a map of all the endangered languages in the world.

223
00:15:45,350 --> 00:15:46,150
Currently,

224
00:15:46,150 --> 00:15:47,590
there are 150

225
00:15:47,590 --> 00:15:48,270
endangered languages

226
00:15:48,270 --> 00:15:49,950
with less than ten speakers,

227
00:15:50,070 --> 00:15:51,310
and 80 endangered languages

228
00:15:51,310 --> 00:15:52,910
with less than five speakers.

229
00:15:52,910 --> 00:15:54,310
Of which, 28 languages

230
00:15:54,310 --> 00:15:56,190
are considered critically endangered languages,

231
00:15:56,190 --> 00:15:57,720
with just one speaker left.

232
00:15:58,070 --> 00:15:59,790
And their knowledge are limited to only simple words

233
00:15:59,790 --> 00:16:00,650
and sentences.

234
00:16:02,510 --> 00:16:04,390
Many languages are disappearing.

235
00:16:04,390 --> 00:16:05,230
Cheng Yao.

236
00:16:05,710 --> 00:16:07,510
You can't save all of them alone.

237
00:16:14,190 --> 00:16:15,650
What are you trying to say?

238
00:16:15,710 --> 00:16:17,190
Let's work hard together.

239
00:16:18,360 --> 00:16:19,750
Machine translation

240
00:16:19,870 --> 00:16:21,870
may not replace human translation.

241
00:16:22,110 --> 00:16:24,150
But machines are the best vehicles

242
00:16:24,150 --> 00:16:25,310
for preserving language.

243
00:16:25,310 --> 00:16:26,510
Besides,

244
00:16:26,510 --> 00:16:27,470
Yuyi is also equipped with

245
00:16:27,470 --> 00:16:29,270
experimental systems that are advanced domestically and internationally,

246
00:16:29,270 --> 00:16:30,310
to help you with

247
00:16:30,310 --> 00:16:32,510
the construction of multimodal speech recognition models and more.

248
00:16:32,510 --> 00:16:34,120
If you want,

249
00:16:34,120 --> 00:16:35,110
you can also be assigned

250
00:16:35,110 --> 00:16:35,990
your own team,

251
00:16:35,990 --> 00:16:36,870
to help you achieve

252
00:16:36,870 --> 00:16:37,790
what you want.

253
00:16:43,830 --> 00:16:44,590
But if you want me

254
00:16:44,590 --> 00:16:46,450
leave Huasheng at this juncture,

255
00:16:47,910 --> 00:16:49,510
I won't be able to face Lin Xi.

256
00:16:52,470 --> 00:16:53,510
I understand.

257
00:16:55,830 --> 00:16:57,030
Let me put it this way.

258
00:16:57,710 --> 00:16:58,870
Previously, due to the lack of demand

259
00:16:58,870 --> 00:17:00,550
for minority languages,

260
00:17:00,750 --> 00:17:02,270
the board has been cutting

261
00:17:02,270 --> 00:17:03,630
the budget for development.

262
00:17:03,630 --> 00:17:05,230
If we can't resolve

263
00:17:05,230 --> 00:17:06,190
the issues with minority language translation

264
00:17:06,190 --> 00:17:07,430
before the Consumer Products Expo,

265
00:17:07,430 --> 00:17:08,630
the Board will definitely

266
00:17:08,630 --> 00:17:09,869
change the direction of development,

267
00:17:09,869 --> 00:17:12,030
and completely give up on the field of minor language.

268
00:17:12,030 --> 00:17:13,950
That's why Xiao is so anxious.

269
00:17:14,150 --> 00:17:15,950
He wants to take advantage of the Expo

270
00:17:15,950 --> 00:17:17,470
and prove to the Board

271
00:17:17,470 --> 00:17:19,470
the importance of minor languages.

272
00:17:20,230 --> 00:17:21,109
Cheng Yao,

273
00:17:21,710 --> 00:17:23,790
We desperately need your help.

274
00:17:34,870 --> 00:17:37,330
This collaboration is a win-win situation.

275
00:17:38,070 --> 00:17:38,990
No one is more suitable

276
00:17:38,990 --> 00:17:40,110
than you.

277
00:17:40,190 --> 00:17:43,140
[Employment Contract]

278
00:17:59,200 --> 00:18:00,270
Yaoyao.

279
00:18:00,510 --> 00:18:02,750
Come and try the new beans.

280
00:18:07,590 --> 00:18:08,510
What's wrong?

281
00:18:09,750 --> 00:18:10,710
Nothing.

282
00:18:23,110 --> 00:18:23,910
Try it.

283
00:18:25,070 --> 00:18:25,950
Thank you.

284
00:18:27,020 --> 00:18:29,750
