287
00:18:33,670 --> 00:18:34,930
I am just taking a look.

288
00:18:36,990 --> 00:18:38,350
Which company is this?

289
00:18:38,870 --> 00:18:39,710
It's Yuyi.

290
00:18:40,190 --> 00:18:42,450
Artificial intelligence translation?

291
00:18:42,910 --> 00:18:44,390
